From: Jakub Roztocil <jakub@roztocil.co>
Date: Mon, 24 Jun 2019 12:19:29 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Changed the way the output filename is generated

When ``--download`` without ``--output`` results in a redirect,
now only the initial URL is considered, not the final one.
---
 CHANGELOG.rst           |  4 +++-
 README.rst              | 20 ++++++++++++----
 httpie/downloads.py     | 52 ++++++++++++++++++++++++-----------------
 tests/test_downloads.py | 14 +++++++++++
 4 files changed, 64 insertions(+), 26 deletions(-)

